                    <span>Any network engineer who is responsible for designing, building and maintaining networks will find this book useful. The author shares valuable design scenarios applicable for any environment. There seems to be a shortage of quality network engineering books covering proper network design. THIS BOOK CLOSES THE GAP!</span>
                  
              
